<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1544,1715]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,548,1580,1607]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Report associated with sponges:</emphasis>
This species was collected from Ross and Weddell Sea in littoral, bathyal area from hydrozoans and sponges (
<bibRefCitation author="Bartsch, I." box="[612,767,1616,1643]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" pagination="185 - 217" refId="ref13010" refString="Bartsch, I. (1990) Antarctic Halacaroidea (Acari): Genera Agaue, Bradyagaue, and Halacarellus. Antarctic Research Series, 52, 185 - 217. https: // doi. org / 10.1029 / AR 052 p 0185" type="journal article" year="1990">Bartsch 1990</bibRefCitation>
; Newell 1984). This species was reported among 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Newell" baseAuthorityYear="1984" class="Hexactinellida" family="Rossellidae" genus="Rossella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lyssacinosida" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="antarctica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Rossella antarctica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Topsent" baseAuthorityYear="1916" box="[365,743,1652,1679]" class="Hexactinellida" family="Rossellidae" genus="Anoxycalyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lyssacinosida" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="joubini" subGenus="Scolymastra">
<emphasis box="[365,494,1652,1678]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Anoxycalyx</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[510,648,1652,1678]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Scolymastra</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[664,743,1652,1678]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">joubini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(cited as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Topsent" baseAuthorityYear="1916" box="[850,1074,1652,1678]" class="Hexactinellida" family="Rossellidae" genus="Scolymastra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lyssacinosida" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="joubini">
<emphasis box="[850,1074,1652,1678]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Scolymastra joubini</emphasis>
