<bibRefCitation author="Bartsch, I." box="[253,407,1688,1715]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" pagination="121 - 128" refId="ref13345" refString="Bartsch, I. (1995) Halacarellus obsoletus n. sp. (Arachnida: Acari: Halacaridae), an associate with Antarctic hexactinellid sponges. Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum in Berlin, 71, 121 - 128. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnz. 19950710113" type="journal article" year="1995">Bartsch 1995</bibRefCitation>
